hy the\ntiming analysis fails. Two $\\gamma$-ray peaks along the orbit are predicted by\nthe two-peak accretion model for an eccentric orbit, that was proposed by\nseveral authors for LS I +61{\\deg}303.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Dec 2014 15:29:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-08"}
