complete. As a concrete quantum formulation of gravity coupled with\nmatter, the ICQFT is about quantum information dynamics for spacetime and\nmatter and eliminates the conceptual obstacles of existing quantum gravity\ntheory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Dec 2014 13:29:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2015 07:55:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 May 2015 15:46:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 29 Aug 2015 17:27:09 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 2 Aug 2017 14:11:22 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 1 Jan 2019 17:22:28 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 2019 15:50:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-04"}
